      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical version control, regression testing, and release documentation satisfy Gradation 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "Commercial FEA solver (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2) with documented QA processes, version control, and regression test suite. FDA-validated solver release used throughout the study."
