      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark problems with known analytical solutions demonstrate correct implementation of linear elastic constitutive models and contact algorithms.",
      "rationale": "Cantilever beam and Hertzian contact benchmark problems solved; results agree with analytical solutions to within 0.5%. Code verification is satisfied at Gradation 2."
